title: Kenny Nightingale Discography 2012-2012 (2 Releases)
description:
--------------------------------------------------------------
KENNY NIGHTINGALE DISCOGRAPHY
--------------------------------------------------------------

This discography may or may not be complete.  It contains the following 2 releases...

 * 2012 - Dear God - Single
 * 2012 - Gospel Got Jazz

These gifts and talents that has been bestowed upon Nightingale to play soul touching melodies with his saxophones,even through the sounds of his voice will leave an extraordinary change upon your life. So, as you listen to the sounds of one of heavens musical gifts I know that your spirit will find comfort within. Mr. Nightingale takes pride in touching others with sweet melodies that has been given to him from above. He's not only intending on reaching the saved, but the lost as well. He has been filled with a passion and love for music. That alone has confirmed to him that playing angelical sounds of gospel jazz with a unique blend form all parts of the world is what God has commissioned him.

Blessings,
TorrentTracts - October 2013
